  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a large mixing bowl, whisk together eggs, sugar, heavy cream, vanilla extract, cinnamon, and allspice.",
    "Add the cubed panettone to the bowl and toss until the bread is evenly coated with the egg mixture.",
    "Pour the mixture into a 9x13-inch baking dish.",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes or until the top is golden brown and the pudding is set.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 10 minutes before serving."
